<p class="indent2" style="-uslm-lc:I13" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">The Secretary shall assess and collect the amount of restitution under an order pursuant to <ref href="/us/usc/t18/s3556">section 3556 of title 18</ref>, United States Code, for failure to pay any tax imposed under this title in the same manner as if such amount were such tax.</p>
